ext-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: verdana, 'lucida sans regular', 'lucida sans unicode', arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34,34,34); line-height: 1.8em;\">Writing: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t</span>Offend<br />\n\tTo offend means to annoy or to anger others. What or who is offending? What or who is offended? Why?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They were offended... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) offending language<br />\n\t2) offending gesture<br />\n\t3) offending the host<br />\n\t4) offending the other party<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tGiven that everyone was working for the same company, even in different departments, a little courtesy was perhaps expected. Shawn was not offended, just a little surprised, so he peeked down the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/stairwell\" target=\"_blank\">stairwell</a>, and saw the figure disappears down the steps. The person was wearing a dark windbreaker and a cap. Since the cap was pushed down, the person's face was covered by shadows, not to mention that whoever it was kept the head down. During the brief encounter, Shawn caught a glimpse of the cap the person was wearing.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167426401433/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p774876/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p774876\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p775984/\">最适合练英音和口语的4部英国电影！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p777057/\">X战警红毯秀大表姐又摔 这已经是第四次了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776750/\">9件小事告诉你：另一半依然疯狂地爱着你</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776902/\">我们来聊聊美队男友 还有那6个没吃上的李子</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776730/\">最值得去的公司 有这5个特征</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p777051/\">当英国考试难哭学生 看他们的家长如何反应</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776804/\">KFC星巴克costa：喝哪家的咖啡最容易胖？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776890/\">地道口语：在美国点披萨的时候要这么说</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776883/\">美剧台词：无论你多大 都需称之为家的地方</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776946/\">囧研究：英语有一天会统治世界吗？</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=